ord-break: break-all; font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(91, 40, 12); font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; "><span style="color: rgb(91, 40, 12); font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; ">僕は・・・</span><br style="word-break: break-all; font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(91, 40, 12); font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; "><span style="color: rgb(91, 40, 12); font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; ">こんなに　こんなに　こんなに　大切な君を</span><br style="word-break: break-all; font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(91, 40, 12); font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; "><span style="color: rgb(91, 40, 12); font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; ">守りたい　守りたい　君だけを</span><br style="word-break: break-all; font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(91, 40, 12); font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; "><span style="color: rgb(91, 40, 12); font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; ">何度も　何度も　何度も　君の名前を</span><br style="word-break: break-all; font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(91, 40, 12); font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; "><span style="color: rgb(91, 40, 12); font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: left; ">呼ぶよまた巡り会うために</span>
